RWPA - Reader Writer Processes Application
==========================================

A C application for demonstrating the consumer-producer problem.
It utilizes POSIX multi-processing, semaphores, shared memory, and signals.
Tested on Linux.


Licence
=======
RWPA is licenced under GPLv3.


Dependencies
============
GCC
Scons


